item.title: Visual Studio 2010 and .NET 4 release candidates available for download
item.dc:creator: SQLDenis
item.description: Visual Studio 2010 and .NET 4 release candidates are available for download Right now the downloads are only available to MSDN subscribers. On Wednesday February 10th the downloads will also be available to the general public You can find the download links here: http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/vstudio/dd582936.aspx
item.content:encoded:
Visual Studio 2010 and .NET 4 release candidates are available for download
Right now the downloads are only available to MSDN subscribers. On Wednesday February 10th the downloads will also be available to the general public

You can find the download links here: http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/vstudio/dd582936.aspx
